#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""
QUIRRELY STATS (qstats) - Comprehensive System & Security Metrics
Version: 1.0.0

Provides real-time insights into:
- Security posture and threat status  
- User authentication and session metrics
- Feature gate usage and access patterns
- Meta events and user behavior
- LNCP Meta/Observers system health and auto-optimization
- Observer metrics: achievement, retention, bundle, progressive, blog/SEO
- Frontend QA: 10 profiles × 4 stances × 5 countries
- Adaptive dashboard performance across regions
- System performance and health
- Database and cache statistics
- WebSocket connections and admin access

Usage:
    qstats                  # Show all metrics
    qstats security         # Security-focused view
    qstats users            # User and auth metrics 
    qstats features         # Feature gate statistics
    qstats performance      # System performance
    qstats events           # Meta events summary
    qstats meta             # LNCP Meta/Observers system health
    qstats observers        # Same as meta view
    qstats frontend         # Frontend QA & UX metrics
    qstats qa               # Same as frontend view
    qstats matrix           # 10×4×5 comprehensive matrix
    qstats funnel           # Marketing funnel & conversions
    qstats live             # Live monitoring mode
    qstats --json           # JSON output for automation
    qstats --help           # This help message

Environment Variables:
    QSTATS_DB_URL          # Database connection string
    QSTATS_REDIS_URL       # Redis connection string  
    QSTATS_LOG_LEVEL       # Logging level (INFO/DEBUG/ERROR)
"""

